cross: Phalaenopsis Ming-Hsing Eagle x Phalaenopsis Sogo Yukidian
exhibitor: Lung Ting Life Sciences Co., Ltd.
location: National Cheng Kung University Fall Orchid Show, Taiwan

measurements.description: Nine flowers and two buds on one 84-cm arching inflorescence; sepals and petals white overlaid shell pink, petals almost touching; lip white, burgundy stripes at base, midlobe white overlaid yellow center and edge, burned orange basally, side lobes white overlaid yellow edge, callus yellow, speckled burgundy; anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
